            <p>10 distinct sensation patterns with adjustable intensity levels, from subtle (27Hz) to powerful (82Hz).</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-number">3</div>
          <div class="step-content">
            <h3>Ergonomic Design</h3>
            <p>360° form-fitting design with flexibility to accommodate different preferences and ensure complete comfort.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
